# ==========================================================================
# Monorepo TrailUp - .gitignore consolidado
# Cada subprojeto (api / frontend / microservice / mobile) mantém o seu
# .gitignore proprio; este arquivo cobre artefatos comuns na raiz.
# ==========================================================================

# --- Dependencias ---
**/node_modules/
**/.venv/
**/venv/
**/__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.egg-info/

# --- Builds / saidas ---
**/dist/
**/dist-ssr/
**/build/
**/web-build/
**/coverage/
*.tsbuildinfo

# --- Caches de ferramentas ---
**/.expo/
**/.metro-health-check*
**/.pytest_cache/
**/pytest-cache-files-*/
**/.kotlin/

# --- Ambiente / segredos ---
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example

# --- Logs ---
*.log
**/logs/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*
**/uvicorn.*.log

# --- Editores / IDEs / ferramentas locais ---
**/.history/
**/.claude/
**/.idea/
.vscode/*
!.vscode/extensions.json
**/.DS_Store
*.suo
*.sw?

# --- Mobile (Expo / nativo) ---
mobile/ios/
mobile/android/
*.jks
*.p8
*.p12
*.key
*.mobileprovision
*.pem

# --- Bancos de dados locais ---
*.db
**/db.sql

# --- Arquivos temporarios de trabalho ---
**/tmp_*.txt
**/_omnicontent-ai/
